title: Area Sports Calendar, 9/27/15
text: NOTE: Schedules provided by schools and are subject to change. High school volleyball: Camelback at Casa Grande Union, 6 p.m. High school volleyball: Vista Grande at Canyon del Oro, 6 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Phoenix at Central Arizona, 7 p.m. THURSDAY High school swimming: Casa Grande Union versus Poston Butte at Palm Island pool, 4 p.m. High school volleyball: Empire at Casa Grande Union, 6 p.m.; Desert View at Vista Grande, 6 p.m. FRIDAY High school football: Flagstaff at Vista Grande; Casa Grande Union at Fountain Hills; Maricopa at McClintock; Coronado at Coolidge; Florence at Combs; Veritas at Santa Cruz. All games begin at 7 p.m. High school cross country: Vista Grande and Casa Grande Union in Desert Twilight Festival at Grande Sports World.
